title: Bobby Made Friends With A Celebrity + We Give Out Our Own TV Emmy Awards + Bobby's Awkward Encounter With Hootie And The Blowfish
itunes:title: Bobby Made Friends With A Celebrity + We Give Out Our Own TV Emmy Awards + Bobby's Awkward Encounter With Hootie And The Blowfish
description:
Bobby tells us who he met that turned out to be a really nice person. The Emmy’s were last night…so we give our own awards out to our favorite TV shows in 4 different categories. Bobby finally met all of Hootie and The Blowfish and had an awkward moment with one of the members. Plus, more stories from our iHeartRadio Music Festival.
